🌟 Project Showcase: To-Do List Web App 🌟

I recently built a responsive To-Do List web application using Flask, MySQL, and Bootstrap! This app allows users to:

🔹 Add and manage tasks
🔹 Enjoy a clean, responsive UI with Bootstrap

Key Highlights:
Backend: Flask for seamless routing and task handling
Database: MySQL to store and manage task data
Frontend: Bootstrap for responsive and modern design
This project improved my understanding of full-stack web development, including integrating Bootstrap for a better UI/UX and handling CRUD operations with Flask and MySQL.
